"<strong>DeepL</strong> automatic translation is available as a <a "
"href=\"%1$s\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"%2$s\">%2$s</a>."
msgstr ""
"<strong>DeepL</strong> automatski prijevod dostupan je kao <a href=\"%1$s\" "
