msgid "Automatically Translate Slugs"
msgstr "Automatski prevedi slugove"

#, tp-ctx-742ebaa7, tp-ctx-7832384c, tp-ctx-e9944eb3
msgid ""
"Generate automatic translations of slugs for posts, pages and Custom Post "
